Follow these rules:

1. Always use const. Never use let or var.
2. Always use immutable data structures and methods.
3. This project uses Deno 2.4.0. Always use the latest Deno and TypeScript
   features.
4. Always use Clean Code and Clean Architecture principles.
5. Always use SOLID principles.
6. Always use the Deno style guide
   https://docs.deno.com/runtime/contributing/style_guide/
